'''2016年帛琉大選'''將在2016年11月1日舉行，選出候任[[帛琉總統|帛琉總統]]及[[帛琉國會|帛琉國會]]議員<ref>[https://palauelection.org/election-dates/ Election Dates] {{Wayback|url=https://palauelection.org/election-dates/ |date=20160822090946 }} Palau Election Commission</ref>。

==總統選舉==
時任總統[[湯米·雷蒙傑索|湯米·雷蒙傑索]]尋求連任，他的小舅子、參議員[[惠恕仁|惠恕仁]]也參選總統。

2016年11月4日，雷蒙傑索以78票領先惠恕仁<ref name=rnzi>{{cite news |first= |last= |title=Slim lead for incumbent in Palau election - Absentee votes to decide result |url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/317315/slim-lead-for-incumbent-in-palau-election-absentee-votes-to-decide-result |work=[[Radio_New_Zealand_International|Radio New Zealand International]] |publisher= |date=2016-11-04 |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archive-date=2016-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105132330/http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/317315/slim-lead-for-incumbent-in-palau-election-absentee-votes-to-decide-result |dead-url=no }}</ref>，到11月10日政府宣布雷蒙傑索以255票擊敗惠恕仁獲連任<ref>{{cite news|title=Remengesau holds on to Palau presidency|url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/317805/remengesau-holds-on-to-palau-presidency|accessdate=11 November 2016|work=Radio New Zealand|date=10 November 2016|archive-date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111151804/http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/317805/remengesau-holds-on-to-palau-presidency|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

