==選舉制度==
帛琉總統選舉採用[[兩輪選舉制|兩輪選舉制]]<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2250/ Palau] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2250/ |date=20161015133331 }} IFES</ref>；{{le|帛琉眾議院|House of Delegates of Palau}}16名議員以[[帛琉行政區劃|各州]]作單議席選區用{{le|簡單多數決|First-past-the-post voting}}選出<ref>[http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2243_B.htm Electoral system] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2243_B.htm |date=20160422115455 }} Inter-Parliamentary Union</ref>；而{{le|帛琉參議院|Senate of Palau|參議院}}11名議員則從全國單一選區中以[[全票制|全票制]]選出，每名選民有13票<ref>[http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2244_B.htm Electoral system] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2244_B.htm |date=20160324094856 }}  Inter-Parliamentary Union</ref>，是屆參議院議員由13名減至11名<ref name=rnzi/>。

